quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,135,"Yahuud en mbi'i ngol leГұol: ngonee yahuud en ndewon laawol peewal, nasaara en mbi'i: ngonee nasaara en ndewon laawol peewal. Jaabo Й“e - Aan Annabiijo - mbi'aa: nganndee minen min ndewata ko diine Ibrahiima peewЙ—e Й—e, o jeyaaka e renndinnooЙ“e Alla e goЙ—Й—o."
  2,136,"Mbi'ee - onon goonЙ—inЙ“e - YahudeeЙ“e e nasaara en joomen nduu noddaandu bonndu: min ngoonЙ—inii Alla e Kur'aan jippinaaЙ—o e amen, min ngoonЙ—inii ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Й“iЙ“Й“e makko Ismaa'iila e Ishaak e Yaakuuba, min ngoonЙ—inii Tawreeta nde Alla addani Muusaa, e Injiila nde Alla addani Iisaa, min ngoonЙ—ini defte Й—e Alla addani AnnabaaЙ“e fof, min ceerndataa hay gooto e maЙ“Й“e, nganndee kamЙ“e fof minen Й“e ngoonЙ—ini, ko ceniiЙ—o gooto O tan min njaЙ“ani e yankinaare."
  2,137,"So Yahuud en e Nasaara en e heeferЙ“e woЙ“Й“e ngoonЙ—inii wano goonЙ—inal mon ngal, tawa Й“e peewii e laawol pooccingol ngol Alla welaa, so Й“e caliima goonЙ—inde, Й“e penni AnnabaaЙ“e fof wolla yoga e maЙ“Й“e, ndeen Й“e ngoni ko e luutondiral e gaГұondiral, taa mettin - Aan Annabi - maa Alla danndu ma tooГұe maЙ“Й“e, O haЙ—an maa bone maЙ“Й“e, O walle, Kanko woni nanoowo haalaaji mume en, gannduЙ—o enniyaaji e golle mum en."
  2,138,"Ndoono-Й—ee e diine Alla Й—e O tagiri on peeГұndi e cuuЙ—iindi mum, alaa diine Й“urЙ—e diine Alla Й—e, kanje jahdi e neesu, gaddooje moЖҙЖҙereeji, kaЙ—ooje bonnere, mbi'ee: minen ko Alla Gooto O tan min ndewata, min ndenndintaa e Makko hay gooto."
  2,139,"Wii - Aan Annabiijo - mbela on njeddondirat e amen - onon yimЙ“e deftere - wonde ko onon Й“uri min haandude e Alla e diine Makko Й—e; sabu diine mon Й—e e deftere mon nde ngadii, Й—uum noon nafataa on, enen fof ko Alla woni jooma men, on naamnetaake golle amen, min naamnetaake golle mon, gooto kala ko golle makko yoЙ“etee, miЙ—en ndewa Alla ko laaЙ“i min ndenndintaa e Makko hay huunde."
  2,140,"Mbela on mbi'at - onon yimЙ“e deftere -: wonde Ibrahiima e Ismaa'iil e Ishaak e Yaakuub e AnnabaaЙ“e iwЙ“e e Й“iЙ—Й—o Yaakuub, ngonndoo ko e laawol Yahuudaagu e Nasaaraagu? Wii Й“e - Aan Annabiijo -: ko onon Й“uri anndude wolla Alla?! so tawii Й“e cikkii wonde Й“een ngonndoo ko e laawol maЙ“Й“e ndeen tawa Й“e pennii; sabu jibineede e maayde maЙ“Й“e wonndoo ko ado jippaade Tawreeta e Injiila! Anndaama ko fenaande Й“e kaalta e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko, Й“e cuuЙ—i goonga jippiiЙ—o dow maЙ“Й“e, alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұe oon cuuЙ—Й—o seedanfaagu, wano baЙ—al yimЙ“e deftere, Alla noon yeebotaako golle mon, maa O yoЙ“ on Й—e."
  2,141,"Ngool leГұol yawtii ko adii on,engol heЙ“a golle Й—e ngol faggiti, onon ne oЙ—on keЙ“a golle Й—e paggiti-Й—on,on naamnetaake golle maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e ne Й“e naamnetaake golle mon, alaa lettirteeЙ—o bakkaat mbo goЙ—Й—o waЙ—i, alaa naftortooЙ—o golle goЙ—Й—o,nganndee gooto kala yoЙ“etee ko ko waЙ—i."